            . I am an officer, and took him in charge.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner Defence. It was thrown down by me - I did not throw it.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 17.</p>
